Venkateswara Bhakti Patalu Telugu | Vaikunta Ekadashi | Mukkoti Ekadasi Songs

Listen to powerful Venkateswara devotional songs in Telugu, specially curated for Mukkoti Vaikunta Ekadashi. These Tirumala Venkateswara bhakti patalu are highly auspicious to listen on Vaikunta Ekadashi for peace, devotion and spiritual upliftment.

Vaikunta Ekadashi is considered the most sacred Ekadashi, believed to open the Vaikunta Dwaram for devotees. Listening to Venkateswara devotional songs on Mukkoti Ekadasi is believed to remove sins, negativity and past karmas, and bring peace of mind, prosperity and moksha blessings. These Telugu devotional songs create a calm and divine atmosphere, making them perfect for home pooja, temple worship and Ekadashi vratam.

These Venkateswara bhakti songs Telugu are suitable for early morning chanting, fasting days and special worship on Vaikunta Ekadashi and Mukkoti Ekadasi. Devotees regularly listen to Srinivasa Govinda songs for devotion, protection and divine grace.

Vaikunta Ekadasi is considered the most sacred Ekadasi, believed to open the Vaikunta Dwaram for devotees. These Telugu devotional stotrams create a calm and divine atmosphere, making them perfect for home pooja, temple worship and Ekadasi vratam.

snippet.title: AVENGERS: DOOMSDAY (2026) | X-Men Trailer | Marvel Comics | Concept
snippet.description:
#Marvel #Avengers #Avengersdoomsday #ChrisEvans #Robertdowneyjr 
 
üé• Attention viewers! (ITS FAN MADE)
The Avengers: Doomsday trailer teases the most dangerous chapter of the Marvel Cinematic Universe, setting up an epic clash in Avengers Doomsday (2026) as the MCU enters Phase 6. With Robert Downey Jr. rumored as Doctor Doom, the Avengers Doomsday teaser and Marvel trailer hint at a world-ending threat, massive battles, and a powerful new era shaped by Doctor Doom in the MCU. From shocking reveals to a stacked Avengers Doomsday cast, this movie promises to redefine the future of Marvel Studios, bringing comics-inspired chaos, multiversal stakes, and the ultimate test for Earth‚Äôs mightiest heroes.

The inspiration behind this video:
The moment we've been waiting for has finally arrived! In this video, we break down the explosive Avengers Doomsday trailer that just dropped online, confirming the shocking return of Chris Evans as Steve Rogers. While the Avengers Doomsday trailer official release gives us a glimpse of a retired Rogers, leaks of a second Avengers Doomsday teaser featuring Thor and the X-Men are breaking the internet. We analyze every frame of these reveals to understand how Marvel Studios is setting up the ultimate confrontation for Avengers 2026 . From the "Steve Rogers Will Return" title card to the first look at Robert Downey Jr Doctor Doom , we cover everything you need to know about the beginning of Marvel Phase 6 .

We dive deep into the massive Avengers Doomsday cast , which is shaping up to be the biggest ensemble in history. Beyond the Robert Downey Jr MCU comeback as the terrifying Doctor Doom MCU variant, we discuss the leaked footage of Cyclops and the X-Mansion that suggests a multiverse collision of epic proportions. We explore the theories that this Doctor Doom movie will see Victor Von Doom uniting the heroes before betraying them, and how Marvel is weaving storylines from the comics like Time Runs Out and Secret Wars into the Avengers Doomsday movie plot. Is Avengers Doctor Doom a hero, a villain, or something far more complex?

Finally, we look at the road ahead for the Marvel Cinematic Universe and MCU Phase 5 's conclusion. We provide a detailed breakdown of the Doomsday trailer easter eggs, including the connections to The Fantastic Four: First Steps and Avatar: Fire and Ash . Whether you are searching for Dr Doom trailer secrets or just want to see the community's reaction to the Avengers Doomsday hype, this video is your ultimate guide. Don't miss our predictions for who will survive the final battle and our full analysis of the Avengers Doomsday marvel trailer leaks.

snippet.title: Arvind Akela Kallu Ka Bhojpuri Gana | Dhakkan Hatake | Shivani Singh, Trishakar Madhu | Video Song
snippet.description:
Presenting Dhakkan Hatake (‡§¢‡§ï‡•ç‡§ï‡§® ‡§π‡§ü‡§æ‡§ï‡•á ‡§Æ‡§ï‡•ç‡§ñ‡§®) ek aisa Bhojpuri party track hai jo first beat se hi mood set kar deta hai. Arvind Akela Kallu aur Shivani Singh ki awaaz iss song ko energy deti hai, yeh gaana fullon dance aur masti ke liye bana hua hai.

Is video mein Trishakar Madhu ka look aur attitude song ke vibe ko aur strong banata hai, jo is track ko reels, DJ sets aur stage shows ke liye perfect choice banata hai. Lyrics bold hain, fun hain, aur repeat pe sunne ke liye perfect hai. Ye song un logon ke liye hai jo New Year 2025 parties ke liye fresh Bhojpuri DJ song chahte hain, stage show mein ek hi gaane mein full energy pe dance karna chahte hain,aur reels ke liye catchy beat dhoondh rahe hain.

Dhakkan Hatake sirf ek video song nahi hai, ye ek performance track hai, jo speaker, stage aur screen teenon jagah zabardast feel deta hai.

The fifth and final season of the American science fiction horror drama television series Stranger Things, marketed as Stranger Things 5, was released on the streaming service Netflix. The season, which will consist of eight episodes, is being released in three parts. The first volume premiered on November 26, 2025, with the second slated for December 25 and the finale scheduled for December 31. The season was produced by the show's creators, the Duffer Brothers, along with Shawn Levy and Dan Cohen.

The season stars Winona Ryder, David Harbour, Finn Wolfhard, Millie Bobby Brown, Gaten Matarazzo, Caleb McLaughlin, Noah Schnapp, Sadie Sink, Natalia Dyer, Charlie Heaton, Joe Keery, Maya Hawke, Priah Ferguson, Brett Gelman, Cara Buono, Linda Hamilton, and Jamie Campbell Bower. en.description:
Stranger Things 5 | EPISODE 8 PROMO TRAILER | stranger things season 5 episode 8 trailer

Take a Look 'STRANGER THINGS SEASON 5 EPISODE 8 PROMO TRAILER' concept for  NETFLIX  stranger things season 5 episode 8 trailer

The fifth and final season of the American science fiction horror drama television series Stranger Things, marketed as Stranger Things 5, was released on the streaming service Netflix. The season, which will consist of eight episodes, is being released in three parts. The first volume premiered on November 26, 2025, with the second slated for December 25 and the finale scheduled for December 31. The season was produced by the show's creators, the Duffer Brothers, along with Shawn Levy and Dan Cohen.

The season stars Winona Ryder, David Harbour, Finn Wolfhard, Millie Bobby Brown, Gaten Matarazzo, Caleb McLaughlin, Noah Schnapp, Sadie Sink, Natalia Dyer, Charlie Heaton, Joe Keery, Maya Hawke, Priah Ferguson, Brett Gelman, Cara Buono, Linda Hamilton, and Jamie Campbell Bower. Joe Chrest, Jake Connelly, Amybeth McNulty, Nell Fisher, Sherman Augustus, Alex Breaux, and Linnea Berthelsen appear in recurring roles.

Govinda Govinda! üôè‚ú®

snippet.title: Kaala Asla - MC SQUARE | Simran Chaudhary | Nikhil - Swapnil (Official Lyrical Video)
snippet.description:
#KaalaAsla #MCSQUARE

Performed by - MC SQUARE and Simran Chaudhary
Composed by - MC SQUARE and Nikhil - Swapnil 
Produced by - Nikhil - Swapnil
Written By - MC SQUARE

Follow Warner Music India:
INSTAGRAM: https://lnk.to/WMIInstagram
YOUTUBE: https://lnk.to/WMIYouTube
FACEBOOK: https://lnk.to/WMIFacebook
SNAPCHAT: https://lnk.to/WMISnapchat
TWITTER: https://lnk.to/WMITwitter

Lyrics:
Ke dhar rakhya s jholi me?
Ke dhar rakhya tanne jholi me?
Tu karta dole kaand bata beimaan,
Na itni bholi mai,
Ke dhar rakhya s jholi me?
Ke dhar rakhya tanne jholi me?

Dharu kaala asla jholi me,
Chhori kaala asla jholi me,
Kai khele khel khilaad, mai pittal baaz,
Mai khelu goli te,
Dharu kaala asla jholi me,
Dharu kaala asla jholi me,

Re tham kit te ho,
Chhori baislaat,
Ke kaam karo,
Chhori maar kaat,
Ye jo gel khade
Makhya bhai s,
Kyu chaude me,
Ri jamai s,

Tere sheher ki oot lugaad, bane badmas,
Pade sab bori me,

Dharu kaala asla jholi me,
Dharu kaala asla jholi me,
Dharu kaala asla jholi me,
Dharu kaala asla jholi me,

Chhori apne bata de tu haal mkha,
Chhore limit me daat le chaal mkha,
Chhori kate faraari me saal mkha,
Mere beer taar deve khaal mkha,

Mat chaal tu tedhi raah, bata de chaah, samajh gayi thodi me,

Ke dhar rakhya s jholi me,
Ke dhar rakhya tanne jholi me?
Ke dhar rakhya s jholi me?
Ke dhar rakhya tanne jholi me?

Chhore nyu to bata teri khesi bheetar asle kyu?
Heri shauk bhi hai par kaatne pade hai masle nyu,

Chaupaal ke peepal jyun kad lerya,
Tere deshwal ne hai sab bera,
Manne suni tu lambardaran ko hai,
Kaam behem saare kaadhan ko hai,

Mat kare fikar ki baat, bakhat ki jaat yaar ne joti re.

Ke dhar rakhya tanne jholi me?
Dharu kaala asla jholi me,
Ke dhar rakhya s jholi me?
Dharu kaala asla jholi me.
